Package org.greatage.ioc

This package represents all base Great Age IoC container classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Configuration<V> This class represent unordered service configuration that is used by service contributors to configure service instance.
Contributor<T> This class represents service contribution definition that distributively configures services.
Decorator<T> This class represents service decorator definition that distributively decorates services.
Interceptor<T> This class represents service interceptor definition that distributively configures service method advices.
MappedConfiguration<K,V> This class represent mapped service configuration that is used by service contributors to configure service instance.
Module This class represents module definition that is used to build ServiceLocator.
OrderedConfiguration<V> This class represent ordered service configuration that is used by service contributors to configure service instance.
Service<T> This class represents service definition that instantiates service.
ServiceBinder This class represents service bind definition that distributively binds service interfaces to their automatically built instances.
ServiceBindingOptions This class represents service binding options that is returned by ServiceBinder to define service unique id, service scope and is it overrides the existing service.
ServiceLocator This class represents object which can provide access to services by their id, or (when appropriate) by just service interface.
ServiceResources<T> This class represents service resources that may be provided to a service when it initializes, are configurated or are decorated.
ServiceStatus<T> This class represents specific information about service inside the IoC container.
 

Class Summary
AbstractConfiguration<T,V,C> This class represents abstract implementation of all types of service configuration.
ConfigurationImpl<T,V> This class represents default implementation of unordered service configuration.
ContributorImpl<T> This class represents default implementation of service contribution definition that distributively configures services.
DecoratorImpl<T> This class represents default implementation of service decorator definition that distributively decorates services.
InterceptorImpl<T> This class represents default implementation of service interceptor definition that distributively configures service method advices.
InternalServiceStatus<T> This class represents implementation of ServiceStatus that is used for internal services.
InternalUtils This class represents internal utility methods for calculating service dependencies.
IOCModule This class represents base module for Great Age IoC container that configures all needed core services.
MappedConfigurationImpl<T,K,V> This class represents default implementation of mapped service configuration.
ModuleImpl<T> This class represents default implementation of module definition.
OrderedConfigurationImpl<T,V> This class represents default implementation of ordered service configuration.
ScopedBuilder<T> This class represents service builder decorator that builds service using service scope.
ServiceAdditionalResources<T> This class represents ServiceResources proxy implementation that is used for extending its default functionality by adding additional resources.
ServiceBinderImpl This class represents default ServiceBinder implementation that distributively binds service interfaces to their automatically built instances.
ServiceBindingOptionsImpl<T> This class represents default ServiceBindingOptions implementation that is used to define service unique id, service scope and is it overrides the existing service.
ServiceBuilder<T> This class represents service builder that is used for service creation by its service, contributors and decorators definitions.
ServiceBuildResources<T> This class represents service resources proxy that is used during service build phase and adds resulting service configuration as additional resource.
ServiceConfigureResources<T> This class represents service resources proxy that is used during service configure phase and adds service configuration as additional resource.
ServiceDecorateResources<T> This class represents service resources proxy that is used during service decorate phase and adds service instance as additional resource.
ServiceFactory<T> This class represent implementation of service definition that instantiates service.
ServiceImpl<T> This class represent default implementation service definition that automatically instantiates service.
ServiceInitialResources<T> This class represents default ServiceResources implementation that is used for retrieving default service resources such as other services, symbols or specific service logger instance.
ServiceLocatorBuilder This class represents utility that simplifies ServiceLocator building process.
ServiceLocatorImpl This class represents default ServiceLocator implementation that is used as main entry point of Great Age IoC container.
ServiceLocatorStatus This class represents ServiceStatus implementation for ServiceLocator service.
ServiceStatusImpl<T> This class represents implementation of ServiceStatus that is used by default for all services.
 

Exception Summary
ApplicationException This class represents base application exception that is thrown almost everywhere in the application powered with Great Age IoC container.
 

Package org.greatage.ioc Description

This package represents all base Great Age IoC container classes.
